HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 06:18:03 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 10-Oct-96 17:25:49 GMT
Content-length: 7737
Content-type: text/html
