deficit by cutting taxes. It isn't the U.S.  If only Bob Dole were running for Prime Minister of France
he might get a positive spin on his tax cut proposal. Headline from Friday's (September 6) Washington Post:
"France to Cut Taxes $5 Billion in Effort to Reduce Deficit." 
