<CENTER><IMG SRC = "/free/Images/River.gif" WIDTH=413 HEIGHT=253 ALT="Foundation for Research on Economics and the Environment"></CENTER>
<H3 ALIGN=CENTER><Font Color = "#000066"><P>FREE is an educational and research foundation, established to support environmental goals based on individual liberty and responsibility and harmonized with economic prosperity. </Font Color></H3 >
<HR>
<CENTER>
<P>
<A HREF="/free/FREE.mission.html"><IMG BORDER=0 HSpace=10 WIDTH=260 HEIGHT=50 SRC= "/free/Images/Introbtn.gif" ALT="Introduction to FREE"></A> 

<A HREF="/free/ST96/Gift.ST1996.html"><IMG BORDER=0 HSpace=10 WIDTH=260 HEIGHT=50 SRC= "/free/Images/Columnbtn.gif" ALT="Latest John Baden Column"></A> 

<P><A HREF="/free/FREE.activities.html"><IMG BORDER=0 HSpace=10 WIDTH=260 HEIGHT=50 SRC= "/free/Images/Activitiesbtn.gif" ALT="FREE Activities"></A>

<A HREF="/free/FP/FREEPerspectivesIntroX1.html"><IMG BORDER=0 HSpace=10 WIDTH=260 HEIGHT=50 SRC= "/free/Images/FPbtn.gif" ALT="FREE Perspectives newsletter"></A> 

<P><A HREF="/free/FREE.staff.html"><IMG BORDER=0 HSpace=10 WIDTH=260 HEIGHT=50 SRC= "/free/Images/Staffbtn.gif" ALT="FREE Staff"></A>

<A HREF="/free/FREE.archive.html"><IMG BORDER=0 HSpace=10 WIDTH=260 HEIGHT=50  SRC= "/free/Images/Archivebtn.gif" ALT="Online Publication Archive"></A> 

