<DOCOLDNO>IA028-000299-B004-249</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/townhall/special/gingrich.html 204.71.237.92 19970114064147 text/html 16304
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 06:42:07 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 07-Jan-97 20:54:05 GMT
Content-length: 16118
