<DOCHDR>
http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/townhall/character.html 204.71.237.92 19970114064709 text/html 20197
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 06:47:31 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 24-Oct-96 09:47:11 GMT
Content-length: 20010
