<h2>Tim Graham</h2>

Tim Graham has been associate editor of MediaWatch since February 1989, where he is responsible for supervising media analysts and researching and writing studies and Janet Cooke Award articles for Media Watch. Graham is the author of the new book Pattern of Deception: The Media's Role in the Clinton Presidency, which critiques the media's coverage of Bill Clinton from 1991 through 1995.
<p>
Graham is a regular talk-radio spokesman for the MRC. His television appearances include appearances on the Cable News and Business Channel shows "Rivera Live," "Cal Thomas," and "Business Insiders," the Christian Broadcasting Network's "700 Club," PBS's "This is America with Dennis Wholey," National Empowerment Television, and the Ollie North show.
