<html>
<head>
<title>Index of Notable Quotables</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<blockquote>
<center><img src="/mrc/images/nq.gif" alt="Notable Quotables"></center>
<p>
<ul>
<h3>Best of...</h3>
<blockquote>
<li><a href="/mrc/nq/best/96nqbst.html">The Best Notable Quotables of 1996</a>
