<HTML>
<HEAD>
<CENTER><TITLE><b><i>Flash</i></b>: Media Research Center's Monthly Member's Report</TITLE></CENTER>
</HEAD>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" 
<U><CENTER><a name="2flash1-6.html"> <font size="8"><I><center>Media Appearances</center></I> </font size="8"></A>
</B></I> </CENTER></U>
<BR>

<br>
<P><b>The proof is in the press.</b> The MRC's impact is far-reaching. Here's a list of some 
of<I> the newspapers, and radio and television programs which have carried our 
articles, used our research, or covered our events recently:</I>
<P>
<br><h2><center><B>MRC on Television</B></center></h2>,
<br>
C-SPAN,CNN's<I> Crossfire,The Tonight Show with Jay Leno</I>,
CNBC's <I>Business Insiders</I>, Equal Time,
Eyewitness</I> <I>News</I>,
NET's <I>American Family</I>, <I>Capitol 
Watch</I>, <I>Headlines &amp;           
